Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:10.38,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(2726,3143,\1c&H0079888D\bord0)}夜に　しまい込んでしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:16.88,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう　僕らに　いつかは来ないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:23.42,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今溢れて　間もなく崩れ落ちて　しまうなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:30.62,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あの夢も　綺麗にさらわれてしまう　かな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.50,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現実と希望の隙間で人知れず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.51,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}摩耗する体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:40.51,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その抹殺でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:44.97,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾かない雨　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:47.21,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凍てつく空気
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:50.09,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ついに凍った花　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:52.01,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}立ち尽くす空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:59.52,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あの幸せは必要じゃなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:04.67,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ美しい呪いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:10.05,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無邪気に　光さえ千切る情景を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:16.74,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(2500,3500,\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}ただ愛おしい呪いで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:20.72,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}全てをひと間に奪って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:23.51,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}失ってしまうなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:27.06,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}一秒だって永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:31.48,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H0077A48C\blur3\bord1\t(1500,,2000,\bord3\3c&H0093B7A4\blur5)}君に絶望が滲むのを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.29,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009BC195\blur3\bord3)} 見たくない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:10.38,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(2726,3143,\1c&H0079888D\bord0)}被深深关进了长夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:16.88,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}属于我们的明天再也不会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:23.42,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若此刻触碰 转瞬就会崩塌四散的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:30.62,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那梦想 是否也会在迷雾中被裹挟 掠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.50,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在现实与希望的缝隙中 不为人知地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.51,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}日渐磨损的躯体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:40.51,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}纵使将它抹杀殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:44.97,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}雨依然不会干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:47.21,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝结成冰的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:50.09,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}终究 花也被封冻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:52.01,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伫立无言的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:59.52,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那份幸福 原来是不被需要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:04.67,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(2500,3500,\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}不过是美丽的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:10.05,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天真烂漫地 将光芒都撕碎的那情景
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:16.74,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(2500,3500,\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}不过是因这可爱的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:20.72,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}若要将一切在刹那间夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:23.51,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}就此彻底失去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:27.06,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009CFCC5\blur3\bord1)}哪怕一秒也要定格成永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:31.48,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H0077A48C\blur3\bord1\t(1500,,2000,\bord3\3c&H0093B7A4\blur5)}唯独你缓缓渗出的那绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.29,ED-1-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H009BC195\blur3\bord3)}我不愿看到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:42.67,ED-1-JP,,0,0,0,,
